          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1683027752967-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once boiling, reduce to a medium-high heat, then top with the <strong>browned meatballs</strong></p><p>Cook for an initial 8-10 min, stirring occasionally to prevent the spaghetti from sticking to the pot, until it is cooked with a slight bite and the meatballs are cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>While the spaghetti is cooking, grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1683027760724-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1683027760724-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1683027760724-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1683027760724-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1683027760724-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the spaghetti is almost done, reduce the heat to medium and top with <strong>half </strong>the <strong>grated cheese </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) and cook, covered, for a final 2 min or until the cheese has melted – this is your <strong>one-pot tomato spaghetti & meatballs</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1683027769193-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1683027769193-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1683027769193-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1683027769193-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1683027769193-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>one-pot tomato spaghetti & meatballs </strong>with the remaining <strong>grated cheese </strong>sprinkled on top</p><p>Serve the<strong> salad</strong> to the side and top with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a crack of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining basil</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
